summary: WSJ’s Take On the Week co-host Telis Demos and reporter Peter Rudegeair are joined by Chris Hansen, founder and portfolio manager of the hedge fund Valiant Capital Management, to talk about what investors should know about power stocks, which have benefitted from the AI race.
